  <Placemark>
   <name>Marine Weather Statement issued September 27 at 2:49PM EDT by NWS Baltimore MD/Washington DC</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>A few easterly to southeasterly wind gusts of 20 to 25 knots are
possible this afternoon. Inexperienced mariners, especially those
operating small vessels, should exercise extra caution if
navigating the waters during this time.</Snippet>
