   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...Seas 5 to 7 ft expected.

* WHERE...Atlantic Waters of Puerto Rico and USVI from 10 NM to
19.5N.

* WHEN...From noon today to midnight AST Sunday night.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...A pulse of northeasterly swell from Major
Hurricane Humberto will increase seas across the local waters
from this afternoon through the rest of the weekend. Seas are
forecast to build to around 7 feet across the offshore Atlantic
waters by noon.</Snippet>
