   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and steep
seas around 9 ft.

* WHERE...5 nm out from Port Orford south and south out to 55 nm.

* WHEN...Until 2 PM PDT this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Gusty north winds and steep to very steep and
hazardous seas could capsize or damage vessels.

* View the hazard area in detail at https://go.usa.gov/x6hks</Snippet>
