   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and steep
seas around 8 to 9 ft.

* WHERE...All areas, except strongest winds and steepest seas
will be primarily south of Gold Beach from this afternoon and
evening.

* WHEN...Until 2 PM PDT this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds and steep to very steep seas could
capsize or damage vessels. Bar crossing could be treacherous.

* View the hazard area in detail at https://go.usa.gov/x6hks</Snippet>
